1
00:00:00,511 --> 00:00:08,611
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,786 --> 00:00:17,023
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,262 --> 00:00:19,253
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,267 --> 00:00:26,033
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,104 --> 00:00:29,471
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,674 --> 00:00:33,235
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,611 --> 00:00:36,978
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,048 --> 00:00:44,477
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,555 --> 00:00:53,691
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,765 --> 00:01:01,797
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:08,878
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,947 --> 00:01:17,013
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,322 --> 00:01:25,787
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,863 --> 00:01:27,888
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:42,023 --> 00:01:43,513
So what's up, Temari?

16
00:01:47,129 --> 00:01:49,791
He's close. He's just right there.

17
00:01:50,165 --> 00:01:51,655
Dang it! What should we do?

18
00:01:53,769 --> 00:01:54,997
Leave it to me.

19
00:02:29,104 --> 00:02:30,503
That was close.

20
00:02:32,441 --> 00:02:33,874
What was that noise?

21
00:02:36,478 --> 00:02:41,313
An explosion...
Perhaps it was a trap set for Sasuke.

22
00:02:42,484 --> 00:02:44,509
I wonder if he's okay.

23
00:02:45,554 --> 00:02:50,287
Don't worry...
He wouldn't get bumped off so easily.

24
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,589
<i>I sure hope so.</i>

25
00:03:02,537 --> 00:03:05,062
Now then, shall we get started?

26
00:03:05,907 --> 00:03:11,368
Before that, I must have you both
return to your original forms.

27
00:03:12,447 --> 00:03:16,178
Please prepare yourself,
Sarutobi Sensei.

28
00:03:17,052 --> 00:03:22,991
<i>An Unrivaled Match.</i>
<i>Hokage Battle Royale!</i>

29
00:04:05,667 --> 00:04:07,828
With every moment,
they are looking more lively...

30
00:04:08,236 --> 00:04:10,568
What is that... Jutsu?

31
00:04:11,606 --> 00:04:12,698
Reanimation.

32
00:04:13,675 --> 00:04:17,975
It's a Forbidden Summoning Jutsu
that can bring the dead back to this world.

33
00:04:20,348 --> 00:04:24,876
The cost of a regular Summoning Jutsu
is that it uses the blood of the caster.

34
00:04:25,787 --> 00:04:26,811
But I've heard that with this Jutsu,

35
00:04:26,888 --> 00:04:29,948
in order to summon
a dead soul to this world...

36
00:04:30,659 --> 00:04:36,723
the body of a living person is sacrificed
as a container for the soul.

37
00:04:37,766 --> 00:04:41,702
Then, the bodies of those two
are of the sacrificed...

38
00:04:42,304 --> 00:04:43,168
Right...

39
00:04:44,105 --> 00:04:47,871
Perhaps dust and dirt cover
the sacrificial body

40
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:52,037
and take on the original form
of the summoned soul.

41
00:04:52,781 --> 00:04:55,909
And by way of the charm
embedded in the head,

42
00:04:56,284 --> 00:04:58,548
the personality of the soul is killed

43
00:04:59,154 --> 00:05:01,520
and it morphs into no more
than a killing puppet.

44
00:05:04,826 --> 00:05:05,986
They're complete.

45
00:05:07,429 --> 00:05:11,388
They look like how they used
to look more than ever.

46
00:05:12,267 --> 00:05:15,532
Do you know the joy and sense
of accomplishment

47
00:05:15,604 --> 00:05:18,767
of hurting one whom
you once called Sensei?

48
00:05:19,841 --> 00:05:25,143
I prepared this scenario
so that you might know that joy.

49
00:05:25,947 --> 00:05:27,812
So please enjoy it.

50
00:05:53,742 --> 00:05:54,731
Lord Hokage!

51
00:05:55,276 --> 00:05:57,301
Even if the shape and form
are the same...

52
00:05:57,545 --> 00:06:01,379
they're neither the First Hokage
nor the Second!

53
00:06:03,051 --> 00:06:04,678
<i>I...know!</i>

54
00:06:22,203 --> 00:06:23,602
Here I go!

55
00:06:25,240 --> 00:06:27,299
Fire Style: Fire Dragon Flame Bombs.

56
00:06:50,999 --> 00:06:53,058
<i>Water Style. Water Wall.</i>

57
00:07:00,942 --> 00:07:01,670
No way!

58
00:07:02,277 --> 00:07:05,713
To be able to set into motion that level
of Water Style in a place with no water.

59
00:07:06,781 --> 00:07:07,748
I can't believe it.

60
00:07:15,356 --> 00:07:18,553
True to the title of the previous Hokage.

61
00:07:22,397 --> 00:07:24,456
<i>Water Style. Water Shock Wave!</i>

62
00:07:35,043 --> 00:07:36,977
<i>Earth Style. Mud Wall.</i>

63
00:08:42,844 --> 00:08:45,574
<i>Same mighty strength as always.</i>

64
00:08:56,291 --> 00:08:59,727
<i>Having two of you is quite a challenge,</i>
<i>as might be expected...</i>

65
00:09:41,202 --> 00:09:42,169
This is bad.

66
00:09:42,704 --> 00:09:45,195
This is a Hidden Jutsu of the First Hokage.

67
00:09:47,976 --> 00:09:49,443
Hidden Wood Style Jutsu:

68
00:09:54,515 --> 00:09:56,244
Deep Forest Emergence.

69
00:10:39,260 --> 00:10:41,057
His Chakra became a source for life.

70
00:10:42,797 --> 00:10:47,200
Wow... So this is the legendary
Wood Style Ninjutsu of the First Hokage

71
00:10:47,268 --> 00:10:49,964
who brought turbulent times under control
and built the Leaf Village.

72
00:10:55,343 --> 00:10:59,302
You're finally caught... eh, Sensei.

73
00:11:13,061 --> 00:11:15,256
Okay. Everyone's here, right?

74
00:11:15,897 --> 00:11:19,025
Okay everyone, let's evacuate quickly.

75
00:11:23,505 --> 00:11:25,564
Don't rush and don't panic!

76
00:11:26,341 --> 00:11:29,174
What's the matter, Konohamaru?

77
00:11:30,078 --> 00:11:31,739
Does your stomach hurt or something?

78
00:11:32,781 --> 00:11:36,080
No... it's not that.

79
00:11:52,200 --> 00:11:54,065
Ninja Art: Summoning jutsu.

80
00:11:54,503 --> 00:11:55,435
Appear!

81
00:11:55,504 --> 00:11:57,335
Monkey King Enma.

82
00:12:14,089 --> 00:12:17,684
Humph...
Something pesky has appeared, eh?

83
00:12:22,063 --> 00:12:23,826
Old Monkey Enma.

84
00:12:32,674 --> 00:12:36,667
Orochimaru...
I knew this would happen.

85
00:12:38,280 --> 00:12:42,717
You're pathetic, Sarutobi...
It's because you didn't kill him back then.

86
00:12:43,618 --> 00:12:45,142
I'm going to do it now!

87
00:12:46,588 --> 00:12:48,021
It's too late.

88
00:12:51,626 --> 00:12:55,027
Please... Enma!
The Adamantine Nyoi.

89
00:12:56,865 --> 00:12:59,561
Take care of him.
Don't let him transform into that!

90
00:13:03,205 --> 00:13:05,036
Okay... Got it!

91
00:13:14,816 --> 00:13:15,578
Transform!

92
00:13:23,258 --> 00:13:23,883
All right.

93
00:13:30,832 --> 00:13:34,461
Wow... What level of Ninjutsu battle!

94
00:13:35,403 --> 00:13:37,997
This is Hokage level!

95
00:13:39,174 --> 00:13:44,043
Oh well...
Things have finally gotten interesting.

96
00:13:56,057 --> 00:13:58,719
<i>That's one of his Snake Swords.</i>

97
00:14:06,601 --> 00:14:07,966
Let's do it, Enma!

98
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:13,130
No matter how strong the body,
the Snake Sword still hurts.

99
00:15:09,331 --> 00:15:10,127
You're mine!

100
00:15:16,938 --> 00:15:17,870
Lord Hokage!

101
00:15:20,542 --> 00:15:21,474
So foolish...

102
00:15:22,210 --> 00:15:26,203
To think you'd strike without even
using the Shadow Clone Jutsu.

103
00:15:27,415 --> 00:15:28,677
<i>No, that's not it.</i>

104
00:15:29,217 --> 00:15:31,412
<i>It's not that he didn't use it.</i>
<i>He can't use it.</i>

105
00:15:32,420 --> 00:15:35,048
<i>The amount of Chakra the Third Hokage</i>
<i>has differs from the past.</i>

106
00:15:35,757 --> 00:15:39,124
<i>The Shadow Clone Jutsu that</i>
<i>evenly disperses Chakra,</i>

107
00:15:39,194 --> 00:15:41,662
<i>if things go wrong,</i>
<i>would be like throwing away Chakra.</i>

108
00:15:43,465 --> 00:15:45,797
<i>Sure enough, is it age?!</i>

109
00:15:52,073 --> 00:15:54,234
Are you okay, Sensei?

110
00:15:56,077 --> 00:15:57,806
Please hang in there.

111
00:15:59,147 --> 00:16:01,411
You are called...

112
00:16:01,483 --> 00:16:06,250
"the Professor who knows and uses all
of the Jutsu existent in Leaf Village," right?

113
00:16:07,188 --> 00:16:09,986
Please don't disappoint me too much.

114
00:16:14,429 --> 00:16:16,727
Please get up, Lord Hokage...!

115
00:16:16,898 --> 00:16:19,458
And please save the Leaf Village!

116
00:16:19,801 --> 00:16:21,166
Lord Hokage!

117
00:16:23,738 --> 00:16:27,105
Fool... It is too late.

118
00:16:36,785 --> 00:16:38,650
<i>Sarutobi, what's wrong?</i>

119
00:16:39,854 --> 00:16:42,049
<i>You're not your usual self.</i>

120
00:16:42,857 --> 00:16:46,987
<i>It's as if you're good for nothing...</i>
<i>What are you hesitating for?</i>

121
00:16:48,396 --> 00:16:50,387
<i>Now's the time to draw the line.</i>

122
00:16:58,573 --> 00:16:59,938
<i>Orochimaru...</i>

123
00:17:06,181 --> 00:17:08,581
You... fool!

124
00:17:17,325 --> 00:17:18,690
Orochimaru...

125
00:17:19,527 --> 00:17:21,222
This is the end.

126
00:17:21,763 --> 00:17:24,288
I'll snap your neck.

127
00:18:35,336 --> 00:18:36,428
<i>As I thought...</i>

128
00:18:36,504 --> 00:18:40,133
<i>It looks like there's no point if</i>
<i>I don't do something about the soul itself</i>

129
00:18:40,208 --> 00:18:42,540
<i>that is bound by the Reanimation.</i>

130
00:18:44,045 --> 00:18:49,506
<i>If so, all I can do is to use...</i>
<i>the Fourth Hokage's Jutsu.</i>

131
00:18:53,655 --> 00:19:01,118
<i>Lord First Hokage, Lord Second Hokage,</i>
<i>please forgive me for using that Jutsu!</i>

132
00:19:03,398 --> 00:19:08,199
Sensei... it seems you're out of breath.

133
00:19:08,937 --> 00:19:10,564
You've gotten old, haven't you?

134
00:19:10,972 --> 00:19:14,999
I've never seen such a pained look.

135
00:19:19,781 --> 00:19:21,510
What's so funny?

136
00:19:23,051 --> 00:19:24,609
It's quite sad...

137
00:19:25,620 --> 00:19:32,287
Old age beats even you,
once renowned as the god of Shinobi.

138
00:19:38,499 --> 00:19:41,900
What's that...?!
What the heck is going on?

139
00:19:43,938 --> 00:19:46,202
Who the heck is that youth?

140
00:19:48,576 --> 00:19:50,441
Who the heck are you?!

141
00:19:51,679 --> 00:19:54,944
Is it so sudden you can't tell?

142
00:19:55,516 --> 00:19:58,349
It's me. Orochimaru.

143
00:20:00,455 --> 00:20:01,820
It can't be...

144
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:05,120
Have you completed that
Forbidden Jutsu?!

145
00:20:11,165 --> 00:20:14,191
You're a truly frightening,
inhuman monster!

146
00:20:41,296 --> 00:20:42,763
I finally caught up.

147
00:20:45,767 --> 00:20:47,792
This is as far as you guys go.

148
00:20:48,369 --> 00:20:48,960
Dang it!

149
00:20:50,705 --> 00:20:52,570
Sasuke Uchiha.

150
00:20:54,943 --> 00:20:57,002
I won't let you get away now.

151
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:15,789
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

152
00:21:16,231 --> 00:21:27,074
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

153
00:21:37,185 --> 00:21:42,817
<i>Yes, breathe in the air</i>
<i>Lift your face to the sky and jump</i>

154
00:21:42,891 --> 00:21:47,851
<i>If it rains, take a break</i>
<i>Go where the wind takes you</i>

155
00:21:48,229 --> 00:21:53,132
<i>So many regrets</i>
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>

156
00:21:53,201 --> 00:21:58,332
<i>Let's go carve the badges in our chest</i>
<i>Yes, it's Show Time, life begins now.</i>

157
00:21:58,406 --> 00:22:08,577
<i>Everyone makes mistakes</i>
<i>It's nothing to be ashamed about</i>

158
00:22:08,883 --> 00:22:19,316
<i>Don't let this scar be for naught</i>
<i>Walk with a smile</i>

159
00:22:19,394 --> 00:22:29,963
<i>Transform sadness into the wind</i>
<i>and continue to forge on</i>

160
00:22:30,038 --> 00:22:35,601
<i>Forge on strong</i>

161
00:22:47,689 --> 00:22:48,781
Orochimaru...

162
00:22:49,258 --> 00:22:51,192
a genius Ninja who appeared
during the war torn era

163
00:22:51,260 --> 00:22:54,195
and one of a kind in decades.

164
00:22:54,363 --> 00:23:00,029
I wanted to believe that this individual
would succeed my strength and will.

165
00:23:00,335 --> 00:23:04,431
But my naiveté created this situation.

166
00:23:04,973 --> 00:23:09,672
I will bury you now and
correct my old mistake.

167
00:23:10,446 --> 00:23:13,813
Next time, "A Mistake from the Past:
A Face Revealed!"
